---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="工作机会 - 每日手帐">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="加入奈索星联" 
      highlightText="奈索星联"
      description="我们正持续寻找适合我们团队的人才。"
    />
    
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">为什么选择我们？</h2>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 mr-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">弹性工作时间</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                你可以在任何地方任何时间开展工作，只要在ddl之前完成任务即可。
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 mr-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">先进的开发工具</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                奈索星联会提供专业的开发辅助工具和编译环境，帮助你更高效地完成工作。
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 mr-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">具有亲和力的团队氛围</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                无论你是大孩小孩，我们都是一家人。团队内会进行利益分成，高达40%的分成比例。
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-3 mr-4">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">健康第一</h3>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                尽管您身体不适/出现事故，我们都会尊重您的选择。团队福利照常享有。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">招募中的职位</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-16">
            
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">没有找到适合你的岗位？</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
              如果您对您的技能信心十足，或者您有其他的想法和建议，请随时与我们联系。我们欢迎任何有才华的人加入我们的团队。
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">联系我们</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
